{"type": "article", "id": 9731, "title": "可发光背包", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-19T07:18:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000615qNPAwIM7a68nt1Ld.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tArtefact 公司最近推出了一款可以发光的背包，不过背包里面可没有什么电子发光设备，而是靠反射汽车灯光，甚至在非常微弱的灯光条件下，它都可以反射出显眼的白光。白天，这款背包看起来和其他普通背包并没有什么不同，而到了晚上便可以保证骑车人和行人的安全。同时，背包内部配有一个照明灯，打开背包便可以自动照明，让你在晚上打开背包找东西也不会手忙脚乱。<a href=\"http://www.artefactgroup.com/content/work/brakepack/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600061353S7eVbqspigjT4n.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060006142a8zok7AUbqiZfp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000614aj6CAhze4siGdfwM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000614d12uLxSNQEXh3MYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}